data.description: Spacious 4 bedroom 1 bath total brick house located on a cul-de-sac. The seller has freshly painted the interior and updated for the buyer to move-in with little to do. The kitchen has granite countertop, stove, refrigerator, microwave staying. The sliding glass door leads to the fenced rear yard, covered patio, and storage shed. The attached garage is actually 1.5 car. Plenty of room for workbench, storage shelving, etc. This home has a great location near the interstate, shopping, etc. Sellers have extra support added to the patio cover just for WINTER - snow can get heavy on cover. Occupancy can be at closing. Don't miss this great buy!
